casebody.data:
SOUTHERN PACIFIC COMPANY, PETITIONER, v. THE UNITED STATES [No. 46236] [107 C. Cls. 525;

331 U. S. —]

Transportation Act of 1940; shipment of non-combat supplies to War Belocation Centers over land-grant railroads. Petition dismissed.

Plaintiff’s petition for writ of certiorari denied by the Supreme Court June 16, 1947.
